---
title: Fish in Genoise Orange Sauce with Roasted Beets and Green Beans in an Almond Vinaigrette
description: Cod and orange are a match made in France! The buttery orange and dill sauce brings out the flavour in the cod and pairs perfectly with roasted beets. You'll be transported to a bistro in Paris after your first bite!
